}", "payloadType": "InlineBase64"}, {"path": "mashup.pq", "payload": "section Section1;
[DataDestinations = {[Definition = [Kind = "Reference", QueryName = "Sales_DataDestination", IsNewTarget = true], Settings = [Kind = "Manual", AllowCreation = true, ColumnSettings = [Mappings = {[SourceColumnName = "Date", DestinationColumnName = "Date"], [SourceColumnName = "StoreID", DestinationColumnName = "StoreID"], [SourceColumnName = "TransactionID", DestinationColumnName = "TransactionID"], [SourceColumnName = "TransactionType", DestinationColumnName = "TransactionType"], [SourceColumnName = "TimeInt", DestinationColumnName = "TimeInt"], [SourceColumnName = "ProductID", DestinationColumnName = "ProductID"], [SourceColumnName = "UnitPrice", DestinationColumnName = "UnitPrice"], [SourceColumnName = "Qty", DestinationColumnName = "Qty"], [SourceColumnName = "Amount", DestinationColumnName = "Amount"]}], DynamicSchema = false, UpdateMethod = [Kind = "Append"], TypeSettings = [Kind = "Table"]]]}]
shared Sales = let
  RndList = List.Buffer(List.Random(RandomListLength+1, Number.From(InputYearMonth))),
  ProdList = List.Buffer(Products),
  TransactionCountList = List.Buffer({1..AvgTransactionsPerDay*2}),
  ProductCountList = List.Buffer({1..AvgProductsPerTransaction*2}),
  QtyCountList = List.Buffer({1..AvgQtyPerProduct*2}),
  TransactionTypeList = List.Buffer({"Card", "Card", "Card", "Card", "Card", "Cash", "Cash", "Check"}),
  WeekendTimes = List.Buffer(WeekendTimelist),
  WeekdayTimes = List.Buffer(WeekdayTimeList),
  DateList = List.Dates(BeginDate, Duration.TotalDays(EndDate-BeginDate) + 1, #duration(1,0,0,0)),
  #"Converted to table" = Table.FromList(DateList, Splitter.SplitByNothing(), null, null, ExtraValues.Error),
  #"Changed column type" = Table.TransformColumnTypes(#"Converted to table", {{"Column1", type date}}),
  RenameDateColumn = Table.RenameColumns(#"Changed column type", {{"Column1", "Date"}}),
  AddStores = Table.AddColumn(RenameDateColumn, "StoreID", each Stores),
  #"Expanded OpenStores" = Table.ExpandListColumn(AddStores, "StoreID"),
  #"Expanded StoreID" = Table.ExpandRecordColumn(#"Expanded OpenStores", "StoreID", {"StoreID", "Slope","UTCOffset"}, {"StoreID", "Slope","UTCOffset"}),
  #"Added index" = Table.AddIndexColumn(#"Expanded StoreID", "TempIndex", 0, 1, Int64.Type),
  AddTransactionCount = Table.AddColumn(#"Added index", "TransactionCount", each let 
InitCount = TransactionCountList{Number.Mod([TempIndex],AvgTransactionsPerDay*2)},
SlopeFactor = Duration.TotalDays([Date] - #date(2016,1,1))/365 * [Slope] * InitCount,
NewCount = InitCount + Number.Round(SlopeFactor,0),
AvoidNegative = List.Max({20, NewCount})
in 
AvoidNegative),
  AddTransactionList = Table.AddColumn(AddTransactionCount, "TransactionID", each let 
    inputdate = Date.ToText([Date],"YYYYMMDD"),
    inputstore = Text.PadStart(Text.From([StoreID]),5,"0"),
    ListLength = [TransactionCount],
    OutputList = List.Transform({1..ListLength}, each inputdate & inputstore & Text.PadStart(Text.From(_), 5, "0"))
in 
OutputList),
  #"Expanded TransactionID" = Table.ExpandListColumn(AddTransactionList, "TransactionID"),
  #"Removed columns" = Table.RemoveColumns(#"Expanded TransactionID", {"TempIndex", "TransactionCount"}),
  #"Added index 1" = Table.AddIndexColumn(#"Removed columns", "TempIndex2", 0, 1, Int64.Type),
  AddTransactionType = Table.AddColumn(#"Added index 1", "TransactionType", each TransactionTypeList{Number.Mod([TempIndex2],8)}),
  AddTime = Table.AddColumn(AddTransactionType, "TimeInt", each let
thismod = Number.Mod([TempIndex2],1000),
outputtime = if List.Contains({0,6}, Date.DayOfWeek([Date])) 
then WeekendTimes{thismod}
else WeekdayTimes{thismod},
withoffset = outputtime + #duration(0,4 + [UTCOffset],0,0),
timeint = Time.ToText(withoffset, "HHmm")
in 
timeint),
  AddProductCount = Table.AddColumn(AddTime, "ProductCount", each ProductCountList{Number.Mod([TempIndex2],AvgProductsPerTransaction*2)}),
  AddProductList = Table.AddColumn(AddProductCount, "ProductID", each let 
ProdListCount = List.Count(RndList),
ProdCount = [ProductCount],
StartIndex = Number.Mod([TempIndex2], ProdListCount),
OutputList = List.Range(ProdList, StartIndex, ProdCount)
in 
OutputList),
  ExpandProductRecords = Table.ExpandListColumn(AddProductList, "ProductID"),
  ExpandProductIDandPrice = Table.ExpandRecordColumn(ExpandProductRecords, "ProductID", {"ProductID", "UnitPrice"}, {"ProductID", "UnitPrice"}),
  AddQty = Table.AddColumn(ExpandProductIDandPrice, "Qty", each QtyCountList{Number.Mod([TempIndex2],AvgQtyPerProduct*2)}),
  #"Removed columns 1" = Table.RemoveColumns(AddQty, {"TempIndex2", "ProductCount", "Slope", "UTCOffset"}),
  #"Added custom" = Table.AddColumn(#"Removed columns 1", "Amount", each [UnitPrice] * [Qty]),
  ChangeTypesFinal = Table.TransformColumnTypes(#"Added custom", {{"ProductID", Int64.Type}, {"TransactionID", Int64.Type}, {"StoreID", Int64.Type}, {"UnitPrice", Currency.Type}, {"Qty", Int64.Type}, {"TransactionType", type text}, {"TimeInt", Int64.Type}, {"Amount", Currency.Type}} )
in
  ChangeTypesFinal;
shared Products = let 
    Source = Json.Document( Text.FromBinary( Binary.Decompress( Binary.FromText( ""), Compression.GZip ) ) ),
  #"Converted to Table" = Table.FromList(Source, Splitter.SplitByNothing(), null, null, ExtraValues.Error),
  #"Expanded Column1 1" = Table.ExpandRecordColumn(#"Converted to Table", "Column1", {"ProductID", "Product_Name", "Category", "Unit_Price", "Supplier_ID", "Supplier_Name", "LaunchDate", "DiscontinueDate"}, {"ProductID", "Product_Name", "Category", "Unit_Price", "Supplier_ID", "Supplier_Name", "LaunchDate", "DiscontinueDate"}),
  #"Changed Type" = Table.TransformColumnTypes(#"Expanded Column1 1",{{"ProductID", Int64.Type}, {"Product_Name", type text}, {"Category", type text}, {"Supplier_ID", type text}, {"Supplier_Name", type text}, {"LaunchDate", type date}, {"DiscontinueDate", type date}}),
  #"Filtered rows" = Table.SelectRows(#"Changed Type", each [LaunchDate] <= BeginDate and [DiscontinueDate] >= EndDate),
  #"Added custom" = Table.AddColumn(#"Filtered rows", "IDandPrice", each [ProductID = [ProductID], UnitPrice = [Unit_Price]]),
  Custom = #"Added custom"[IDandPrice],
  #"Custom 1" = List.FirstN(Custom, MaxNumberOfProducts)
in
  #"Custom 1";
shared Stores = let 
    Source = Json.Document( Text.FromBinary( Binary.Decompress( Binary.FromText( ""), Compression.GZip ) ) ),
    #"Converted to Table" = Table.FromList(Source, Splitter.SplitByNothing(), null, null, ExtraValues.Error),
  #"Expanded Column1" = Table.ExpandRecordColumn(#"Converted to Table", "Column1", {"City", "StateName", "County_FIPS", "County", "Latitude", "Longitude", "Population", "StoreID", "Manager", "ManagerEmail", "OpenDate", "CloseDate", "State", "Region", "TransactionSlope", "Time Zone", "UTC Offset"}, {"City", "StateName", "County_FIPS", "County", "Latitude", "Longitude", "Population", "StoreID", "Manager", "ManagerEmail", "OpenDate", "CloseDate", "State", "Region", "TransactionSlope", "Time Zone", "UTC Offset"}),
    #"Changed Type" = Table.TransformColumnTypes(#"Expanded Column1", {{"City", type text}, {"State", type text}, {"County_FIPS", Int64.Type}, {"County", type text}, {"Latitude", type number}, {"Longitude", type number}, {"Population", Int64.Type}, {"StoreID", Int64.Type}, {"Manager", type text}, {"ManagerEmail", type text}, {"OpenDate", type date}, {"CloseDate", type date}, {"Region", type text}, {"StateName", type text}, {"TransactionSlope", type number}, {"Time Zone", type text}, {"UTC Offset", Int64.Type}}),
  #"Filtered rows" = Table.SelectRows(#"Changed Type", each [OpenDate] <= BeginDate and [CloseDate] >= EndDate),
  #"Added custom" = Table.AddColumn(#"Filtered rows", "IDandSlope", each [StoreID = [StoreID], Slope = [TransactionSlope], UTCOffset= [UTC Offset]]),
  Custom = #"Added custom"[IDandSlope],
  #"Custom 1" = List.FirstN(Custom, MaxNumberOfStores)
in
    #"Custom 1";
shared InputYearMonth = "202401" meta [IsParameterQuery = true, IsParameterQueryRequired = false, Type = type text, DefaultValue = null];
shared LatestDate = 1000 meta [IsParameterQuery = true, IsParameterQueryRequired = false, Type = type number, DefaultValue = null];
shared BeginDate = let
  InputDate = Date.From(InputYearMonth & "01"),
  MaxDate = List.Max({InputDate, Date.From(LatestDate)})
in 
  MaxDate;
shared EndDate = let
  thisday = Date.From(DateTime.LocalNow()),
  InputDate = Date.EndOfMonth(Date.From(InputYearMonth & "01")),
  MinDate = List.Min({InputDate, thisday})
in 
  MinDate;
shared AvgTransactionsPerDay = 100 meta [IsParameterQuery = true, IsParameterQueryRequired = false, Type = type number, DefaultValue = null];
shared AvgProductsPerTransaction = 20 meta [IsParameterQuery = true, IsParameterQueryRequired = false, Type = type number, DefaultValue = null];
shared RandomListLength = 300 meta [IsParameterQuery = true, IsParameterQueryRequired = false, Type = type number, DefaultValue = null];
shared AvgQtyPerProduct = 4 meta [IsParameterQuery = true, IsParameterQueryRequired = false, Type = type number, DefaultValue = null];
shared MaxNumberOfProducts = 30 meta [IsParameterQuery = true, IsParameterQueryRequired = false, Type = type number, DefaultValue = null];
shared MaxNumberOfStores = 20 meta [IsParameterQuery = true, IsParameterQueryRequired = false, Type = type number, DefaultValue = null];
shared fnGenerateRandNormDateTimes = let
    Source = (inputDT as datetime, count as number, seed1 as number, seed2 as number, mean as number, sd as number) as list=> 
  let 
  startlist = {0..count-1},
  firstseed = List.Buffer(List.Random(count, seed1)),
  secondseed = List.Buffer(List.Random(count, seed2)),
  output = List.Transform(startlist, each (sd * (Number.Sqrt(- 2 * Number.Ln(firstseed{_}))
       * Number.Cos(2.0 * 3.14159265358979323846 
       * secondseed{_} ) ) + mean ) ),
  DTlist = List.Transform(output, each inputDT + #duration(0,0,Number.Round(60*_,0),0))
in 
  DTlist
in
    Source;
shared WeekdayTimeList = let
  Source = fnGenerateRandNormDateTimes(#datetime(2025, 5, 1, 0, 0, 0), 1000, 10, 20, 17, 5),
  Custom = List.Transform(Source, each List.Max({List.Min({Time.From(_), #time(22,0,0)}), #time(7,0,0)}))
in
  Custom;
shared WeekendTimelist = let
  Source = fnGenerateRandNormDateTimes(#datetime(2025, 5, 1, 0, 0, 0), 1000, 11, 12, 11, 6),
  Custom = List.Transform(Source, each List.Max({List.Min({Time.From(_), #time(22,0,0)}), #time(7,0,0)}))
in
  Custom;
shared Sales_DataDestination = let
  Pattern = Lakehouse.Contents([CreateNavigationProperties = false, EnableFolding = false]),
  Navigation_1 = Pattern{[workspaceId = "Workspace_DFMarket_GUID"]}[Data],
  Navigation_2 = Navigation_1{[lakehouseId = "Lakehouse_DF_Market_LH_GUID"]}[Data],
  TableNavigation = Navigation_2{[Id = "Sales", ItemKind = "Table"]}?[Data]?
in
  TableNavigation;
